import React from 'react' export default function Quote(props) { const { backgroundImageUrl, fontFamily, quote } = props; const styles = { backgroundSize: 'cover', backgroundPosition: 'center center', backgroundImage: `url(${backgroundImageUrl})`, fontFamily: fontFamily, width: '400px', height: '400px' } return (
{quote.body}
{quote.author}
) }
